name: Gray 2
description: Sometimes gray reminds of sad moments. Scientists believe that if «gray» takes place in your life is a signal of depression. Do you ever see a gray picture that reminds you of a lonely winter night or something sad? I know that happens to you too. And I think if you’re not a depressed person and you’re just moping around, there’s nothing wrong sometimes to look at the world in grey. It’s cool that we’re human and we can be happy and sad!
